    Dependent hash map lemmas #

    This file contains lemmas about Std.Data.DHashMap.Raw. Most of the lemmas require EquivBEq and LawfulHashable for the key type . The easiest way to obtain these instances is to provide an instance of LawfulBEq .

    source
